elcome|website=New England Base Camp in the Blue Hills near Boston}}</ref>  || Spirit of Adventure Council ||[[Milton, Massachusetts|Milton, MA]]|| Active ||  Formerly Camp Sayre. Open to the public. \n|-\n|Nobscot Scout Reservation\n|Mayflower Council\n|[[Framingham, Massachusetts|Framingham, MA]]\n|Active\n|\n|-\n | Treasure Valley Scout Reservation || Mohegan Council ||[[Rutland, Massachusetts|Rutland, MA]]|| Active || Main entrance is on the Rutland/Paxton line. Part is also in Oakham.\n |-\n | Wild Goose Camp || Boston Council ||[[Barnstead, New Hampshire|Barnstead, NH]]|| Merged || Now T.L. Storer Scout Reservation\n |-\n | T.L. Storer Scout Reservation || Spirit of Adventure Council ||[[Barnstead, New Hampshire|Barnstead, NH]]|| Active || Part of the Spirit of Adventure Council's Northern NeXus.<ref name=\"northernnexus\">{{cite web|url=http://www.joomag.com/magazine/the-northern-nexus-of-adventure/0658419001448639266?page=2|title=The Northern NeXus Of Adventure|publisher=}}</ref>\n|-\n | Parker Mountain Scout Camp || Spirit of Adventure Council ||[[Strafford, New Hampshire|Strafford, NH]]|| Active || Part of the Spirit of Adventure Council's Northern NeXus.<ref name=\"northernnexus\" /> Leased to the Beam Center in NYC during summer for a non-scouting related camp.\n|-\n|Wah-Tut-Ca Scout Reservation || Spirit of Adventure Council ||[[Northwood, New Hampshire|Northwood, NH]]|| Active || Part of the Spirit of Adventure Council's Northern NeXus.<ref name=\"northernnexus\" />\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Michigan ===\n{{Details|Scouting in Michigan}}\n {| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\"\n |-\n ! scope=\"col\" width=\"30%\" | Camp name\n ! scope=\"col\" width=\"20%\" | Council\n ! scope=\"col\" width=\"15%\" | Location\n ! scope=\"col\" width=\"10%\" | Status\n ! scope=\"col\" width=\"25%\"  class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n |-\n |[[Bear Lake Scout Camp]] ||  Summer Trails / Saginaw Bay area / Lake Huron area  || [[Kalkaska, Michigan|Kalkaska]] || Sold ||