en]] || Active ||\n |-\n | [[Goshen Scout Reservation#Camp Bowman|Camp Bowman]] || [[National Capital Area Council]]  || [[Goshen, Virginia|Goshen]] || Active ||\n |-\n | [[Camp Brady Saunders]] || Heart of Virginia ||Goochland\n| Active||\n |-\n | [[Camp Chickahominy]] ||  ||  || ||\n|-\n|Camp Eagle Point\n|Heart of Virginia\n|Boydton\n|Active\n|\n|-\n |[[Camp Lions]]||  ||  ||  ||\n |-\n |[[Goshen Scout Reservation#Camp Marriott|Camp Marriott]]||[[National Capital Area Council]]||[[Goshen, Virginia|Goshen]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[Camp Okee]]||  ||  ||  ||\n |-\n |[[Camp Ottari]]||[[Blue Ridge Mountain Council]]||[[Hiwassee, Virginia]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[Camp Powhatan]]||[[Blue Ridge Mountain Council]]||[[Hiwassee, Virginia]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[Camp Rock Enon]]||[[Shenandoah Area Council]]||[[Gore, Virginia|Gore]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[Camp Roland]]||  ||  ||  ||\n |-\n |[[Goshen Scout Reservation#Camp Ross|Camp Ross]]||[[National Capital Area Council]]||[[Goshen, Virginia|Goshen]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[Camp S. Douglas Fleet]]|| Heart of Virginia ||Richmond\n|Active\n|\n |-\n |[[Camp Shenandoah]]||[[Stonewall Jackson Area Council]]||[[Swoope, Virginia|Swoope]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[Camp Siouan]]||  ||  ||  ||\n |-\n |[[Camp T. Brady Saunders]]||  ||  ||  ||\n |-\n |[[Camp Washington (Virginia)|Camp Washington]]||  ||  ||  ||\n |-\n |[[Camp Waters]]||  ||  ||  ||\n |-\n |[[Chesapeake Bay HA Sailing Experience]]||  ||  ||  ||\n |-\n |[[Claytor Lake Aq. Base]]||[[Blue Ridge Mountain Council]]||[[Hiwassee, Virginia]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[Goshen Scout Reservation]]||[[National Capital Area Council]]||[[Goshen, Virginia|Goshen]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[High Knoll Trail Camp]]||[[Blue Ridge Mountain Council]]||[[Hiwassee, Virginia]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[Goshen Scout Reservation#Camp Olmstead|Camp Olmstead]]||[[National Capital Area Council]]||[[Goshen, Virginia|Goshen]]|| Active ||\n |-\n |[[Peninsula Scout Reservation]]||  ||  ||  ||\n |-\n |[[Pipsico Scout Reservat